#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 0.21.1 released"
msgstr "Quarkus 0.21.1发布"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We just released Quarkus 0.21.1."
msgstr "我们刚刚发布了Quarkus 0.21.1。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As for 0.20.0, to build native executables, you will need GraalVM 19.1.1."
msgstr "至于0.20.0，要构建本地可执行文件，你需要GraalVM 19.1.1。"

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "What's new?"
msgstr "有什么新内容？"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This release is mostly about fixing bugs and usability issues. The link:/guides/kafka-streams[Kafka Streams] and link:/guides/tika[Apache Tika] extensions got their usability greatly improved for instance."
msgstr "这个版本主要是修复错误和可用性问题。例如， link:/guides/kafka-streams[Kafka Streams] 和 link:/guides/tika[Apache Tika] 扩展的可用性得到了极大的改善。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can find https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/0.21.0[the full changelog of 0.21.0] and https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/0.21.1[the few additional issues we fixed in 0.21.1] on GitHub."
msgstr "你可以在GitHub上找到 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/0.21.0[0.21.0的完整更新日志] 以及 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/0.21.1[我们在0.21.1中修复的几个额外问题] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2019-08-15-quarkus-0-21-1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We have a lot of interesting things in the works so stay tuned for our late August and September announcements."
msgstr "我们有很多有趣的事情正在进行中，所以请继续关注我们8月底和9月的公告。"

